snippet: More than 60 trophies won by Red Bull have been stolen in a burglary at the Formula One team’s factory in Milton Keynes, England.
lead_paragraph: More than 60 trophies won by Red Bull have been stolen in a burglary at the Formula One team’s factory in Milton Keynes, England.
